verbose_text: Interestingly, we found that both dOASL and oOASL significantly increased the expression of RNase L and 10 of 16 genes (IRF1, IRF7, IFNalpha, IFNbeta, IFNAR1, JAK1, STAT1, MX1, PKR, and TNFalpha) related to IFN signaling in DF1 OASL-/- cells induced by the CK/0513 virus.
evidence: DF1 OASL-/-  cells induced by the CK/0513 virus
